
---

## Data Access
This project does not use external datasets.

All data is generated dynamically during runtime from the CartPole-v1 environment provided by the Gymnasium library.

No downloads or external files are required.

---

## Code Access / Structure
The project is contained in a single Jupyter Notebook:

- MD_Notebook_Jai'Anni_White_ITAI.ipynb

It includes:
- Environment setup
- Random agent evaluation
- Q-Learning implementation
- Training loop (500 episodes)
- Exploration experiment
- Visualization of results
- Written analysis and reflections

To run:
1. Open in Google Colab or Jupyter Notebook
2. Run all cells from top to bottom
3. Ensure dependencies are installed
